  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, defined cases of COVID-19 with mild, moderate or severe pneumonia will be
      treated with standard treatment regimens in combination with oral administration of
      Colchicine Plus Herbal phenolic monoterpene Fractions. Improvement in clinical, laboratory
      and radiological manifestations will be evaluated in treated patient compared to control
      group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
